verbose_text: Isolates over-expressing AcrAB and AcrADefflux pump systems were selected and the transcriptional expression of the local regulatory gene AcrR were demonstrated by quantitative Real Time PCR using primers (forward primer : 5'ACAAGAAGCGCAAGAAACGC3 ' and reverse primer : 5'CCAGCGAGGTGGATGATACC3 ').
evidence: expression of the local regulatory gene AcrR
